with any applicable general permit issued by the United States Army Corps of Engineers, or as may be necessary to effect
remediation pursuant to the provisions of the Wetlands Restoration and Mitigation Plan submitted as an Exhibit to
this Consent Decree. The civil penalty of $47,500 is intended to cover the violations at both the Peoria County and
Marshall County Sites.
