The Department considered seriously the appropriateness of the fee and awarding a different level of funding to intermediaries
performing a higher level of activities. The Department has chosen a processing fee structure through which each
intermediary will receive a $15,000 start-up fee and five percent of each technical assistance grant it administers,
which will be allocated as the grants are disbursed. Each intermediary will also receive a flat fee of $500 for each
